{"tid":2049911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】約翰遜：立法或嚴重侵害港人政治及公民自由 英冀向港人伸出友誼支持之手","createTime":"2020-06-03T19:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T19:07:34.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c77e892cfb4121af4199cf091b8a29f98ac420b","tid":2049911,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:07:34.000Z","msg":"【港版國安法】約翰遜：立法或嚴重侵害港人政治及公民自由 英冀向港人伸出友誼支持之手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/J5xGgmSMylHFoshGRDQzA4OEFAQ=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XBG3EGAPFXYCYIX64S2MOKY3TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FJ5xGgmSMylHFoshGRDQzA4OEFAQ%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXBG3EGAPFXYCYIX64S2MOKY3TA.jpg&h=c0a5de48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜說，中國在香港的行動，有「嚴重侵害」《中英聯合聲明》保障港人政治自由的風險。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜在周三的疫情簡報會上說：「我認為目前發生的事情，有可能侵害《中英聯合聲明》...保障香港政治與公民自由。目前的立法建議，或將非常、非常嚴重地侵害有關保障。」<br />\n<br />\n他又說：「我們的意思是：我們希望向港人伸出友誼、支持和忠誠之手。」他表示看不出英國對香港的態度，與對中國電訊設備生產商華為的態度有何矛盾之處，英國希望與中國維持「良好、友善和是非分明的工作關係」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200604/46EBKPOTVQFJ6DX7HJWYKANXFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200604%2F46EBKPOTVQFJ6DX7HJWYKANXFQ%2F&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BI5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=22d692a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200604%2F46EBKPOTVQFJ6DX7HJWYKANXFQ%2F&h=2d690c36\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200604/46EBKPOTVQFJ6DX7HJWYKANXFQ/</a>"}]}